                    <a href="https://www.azleg.gov/arsDetail/?title=41" class="a" target="_blank">title 41</a>, chapter 6, article 10. Except as provided in section
                    <span class="s16">41-1092.08</span>
                    <a href="https://www.azleg.gov/arsDetail/?title=12" class="s13" target="_blank">, subsection H, final decisions of the director are subject to judicial review pursuant to</a>
                    <a href="https://www.azleg.gov/arsDetail/?title=12" class="s19" target="_blank"> </a>
                    <span class="s16">title 12</span>, chapter 7, article 6.
                </div>
                
            </li>
            <li>
                <div>On completion of an investigation, the director:</div>
                
                <ol id="l15">
