                    <a href="https://www.azleg.gov/arsDetail/?title=41" class="s19" target="_blank"> </a>
                    <a href="https://www.azleg.gov/arsDetail/?title=41" class="a" target="_blank">title 41</a>
                    <a href="https://www.azleg.gov/arsDetail/?title=41" class="s13" target="_blank">,</a> chapter 6, article 10.
