                    <a href="https://www.azleg.gov/arsDetail/?title=41" class="s19" target="_blank"> </a>
                    <a href="https://www.azleg.gov/arsDetail/?title=41" class="a" target="_blank">title 41</a>, chapter 6, article 10. Notice of the hearing shall be sent by certified mail, return receipt requested, to the licensee&#39;s or registrant&#39;s last known address in the department&#39;s files.
                </div>
                
            </li>
            <li>
                <div>
                    Based on information the board receives during a hearing pursuant to
                    <a href="https://www.azleg.gov/arsDetail/?title=41" class="s19" target="_blank"> </a>
                    <a href="https://www.azleg.gov/arsDetail/?title=41" class="a" target="_blank">title 41</a>, chapter 6, article 10, it may recommend to the director that the director:
                </div>
                
                <ol id="l16">
