                            <u>11-1022</u>
                            <span>for any reasonable costs incurred for the care and maintenance of any animal that was taken to the animal shelter as a result of conduct proscribed by subsection A of this section.</span>
                        </div>
                        
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </li>
            <li>
