                            <a href="#bookmark161" class="s19"> </a>
                            <a href="#bookmark161" class="a">A.R.S. § 32-2622</a>
                            <a href="#bookmark161" class="s32">,</a>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div>Assess the accuracy of the information provided by the applicant,</div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div>Verify proof of U.S citizenship or legal resident status with authorization to seek employment by examining either one document from List A on U.S. Department of Justice Form I-9 or one document from both Lists B and C, and</div>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <div>Ensure that the application includes:</div>
                        <ol id="l276">
